		<div id="tr_9" class="t s2_9">(2) None of its owned or operated facilities to be used in the performance of this contract is subject to the </div>
		<div id="ts_9" class="t s2_9">Form R Filing and reporting requirements because each such facility is exempt for at least one of the </div>
