		<div id="tw_9" class="t s2_9"><lable><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Value_22145_45310 />(i) The facility does not manufacture, process, or otherwise use any toxic chemicals listed in 40  </lable> </div>
		<div id="tx_9" class="t s2_9">CFR 372.65; </div>
